= flash

(from gem actionpack-3.2.9)
=== Implementation from ActionDispatch::Request
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  flash()

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Access the contents of the flash. Use <tt>flash["notice"]</tt> to read a
notice you put there or <tt>flash["notice"] = "hello"</tt> to put a new one.


